Title: Signed V&A Victoria & Albert Museum Pin Brooch Pendant Bow Silver Enamel 9D
Description: This brand new Victoria and Albert Museum inspired brooch/pin & pendant combination is signed V & A. It is silver plated and features crystals and yellow enamel. It measures approximately 2 1/8 inches by 1 3/4 inch. The brooch is inspired by a 1947 silk grosgain dress designed by Victor Steibel with a large bow in the back. The current retail value of these earrings is £125 in the UK (approximately $156 US Dollars).This brand new brooch is new without tags, but will be sent in a gift box. It is sure to make a beautiful gift or be a treasured addition to your collection!
